Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(座敷童子)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(前篇)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:00:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖药的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样很挡路耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你站在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人会进不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找别人跟你买药吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住一晚！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(睽违已久)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(物怪)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色的月光照着你徘徊的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说的话却说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子令人如此不耐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹记那虚伪的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘却那温暖的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有如失了魂的空虚眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照着什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚幻的下弦月隐脏在云间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗如今正慢慢浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,述说着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱着孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚只能够幽幽叹息吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(当晚)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子…你很冷吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很苦吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是中药…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘\N您独自经营这家旅馆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房子\N在我很年轻的时候就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在改成旅馆之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是做什么的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪大了不记得了呐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我借宿一晚呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思我们已经打烊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请去别家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这附近还亮着灯的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是已经客满了啦！\N拜托您哪里都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算让我睡泥巴地也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错！加上你就客满了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么~这个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我…正被人追杀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会没命的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你越讲越扯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这么年轻漂亮的姑娘\N好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面淋雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐人膏又名半助膏药
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很可怜啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再继续淋雨的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子里的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会流产的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怀孕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~真是的真听不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德次你都站几年柜台了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉！我们不想惹麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你快点出去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦走出这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走出这里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会在这家店的门口…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躺着我跟腹中胎儿的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是更麻烦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会被你威胁的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有威胁您！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何\N我都要生下这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是出去外面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就无法保护他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德次，过来\N老板娘拜托您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算我求您好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她带到那个房间去\N求求您行行好！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么~那个房间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没办法嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带她到房间去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去把被子准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:07:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…非常谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明让她睡我房间也是可以的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个房间平常是不安排客人住的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外人也不知道有这个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请你无论如何安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子有点饿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能给我点东西吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在恶作剧啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了…明天再叫德次清掉吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下一些饭团哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经这么晚了说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下就有东西吃了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么想把孩子生下来啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不清楚是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你打算独自抚养他吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确有这个打算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了只能说你太年轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想法比较天真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小婴儿不是只要吃饭就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的出生不受祝福\N你又硬把他生下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时为了养活他遇到困难\N对那孩子来说好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要生下这个孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的年轻人真是固执啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的话才不会…\N老板娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这么不负责任的事哟！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被单应该就快送过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得帮你准备饭团呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您…老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不倒翁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀~卖药的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上个厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去厕所的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那个走廊转个弯就到了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这上面也有房间？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能不过是仓库而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别自已跑上去哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~刚刚买药的钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系明天再给也行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先告辞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护身符…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底掉到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是从哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我还给我还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怀了小宝宝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再四个月就会从这里出来哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很开心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯当然开心罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂~我们去那边好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦！倒是你快点回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:13:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…放过我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果生了男孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后又厚着脸皮出现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷跟夫人…会很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经跟少爷分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管你这个\N不懂人情世故的女人讲什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想把孩子生下来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这样而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都到这里了\N怎么能空手而回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃\N这个孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧！\N这个孩子希望出生到这世上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三更半夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵什么吵啊…真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里？\N这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你干的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪老板娘让她住这房间\N保护她吗？可是…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德次！你去报警！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会没必要？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个人被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而杀死他的人是你…\N不是这个人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手…不是这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被卷住往上飞…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是上面什么都没有，然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转转转转的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转转转转啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖药的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你怎么会在这个房间？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手…并不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自已打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个卖药的\N怎么会带这么恶心的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了斩杀哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斩、斩什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是物怪哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有被什么缠住的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡说八道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看这个尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情人类是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好乖好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里怎么会有那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打哪儿来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就摆在房里的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有个孩子过来拿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁的小孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡说些什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚没有带着孩子的客人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那些脚步声呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有笑声呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘带我来这房间的时候\N也有听到吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没听到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听有这么多孩子的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听那边也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在胡说什么\N这里是顶楼哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更里面的房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边也有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跟这房间有关联的物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩婴儿的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是座敷童子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拔出退魔剑是有条件的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果无法找出“形”、“真”、“理”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么剑就无法拔出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪的“形”\N是基于人的渊源跟因果形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“真”乃事情的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“理”乃心的样貌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道各位的真与理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:21:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请仔细道来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(待续)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你不在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法笑得开怀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此被你吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在随处可见的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些无可取代的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能够好好珍惜地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已经别无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:22:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛开在那片天空下的夏之花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随风缓缓飘落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.89,0:22:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光落在那早已看不见的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子也令人珍爱到无可比喻

